{"tid":2388462,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"以為Rosé「比倒讚」Lisa瞪大眼瞬間變臉！可愛表情變化全被拍","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:01:09.000Z","uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7aee7d10cf926916df477754ed19f827f3b3b9ce","tid":2388462,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:57:14.000Z","msg":"南韓女團BLACKPINK的Lisa被捕捉到一個瞬間變臉的表情，但得知原因後讓不少網友直呼「太可愛！」原來是她們接受訪問的時候，旁邊隊友Ros&eacute;突然伸出手來「比倒讚」，讓Lisa瞪大眼睛備感驚訝，但後來理解真正意義後，她才露出燦笑，表情變化都被鏡頭給拍了下來！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/d5431090.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2Fd5431090.jpg&h=a92bfe58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲以為Ros&eacute;「比倒讚」Lisa瞪大眼瞬間變臉。（圖／翻攝自AbemaTV）<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK在2018年曾經接受日本節目訪問，長達46分的訪談在逼近結束之時，主持人問了每個人今天訪問的感想，輪到Lisa發言時，她說，「本來很緊張，其實我們4個人都很緊張，但看到粉絲（追直播）為我們加油，緊張感就緩解了許多。」<br />\n<br />\nLisa趁著日文翻譯的時間，對著鏡頭比出大拇指按讚、做著開心期待的表情，這時候坐在她旁邊的Ros&eacute;突然伸手比出「拇指向下」，彷彿對她倒讚，她看到超震驚，立即瞪大眼睛轉頭，Ros&eacute;趕緊示意動了幾下，她才會意張嘴發出「啊～」，原來Ros&eacute;是要跟她合比一個愛心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/d5431091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2Fd5431091.jpg&h=6581fec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Lisa下秒心電感應，才理解Ros&eacute;是要跟她合比一個愛心。（圖／翻攝自AbemaTV）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/d5431092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2Fd5431092.jpg&h=eb0ef925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時候的Lisa從委屈臉轉成燦爛笑容，伸出自己的手與Ros&eacute;的倒讚合體，顯得相當滿意。不過因為是直播節目，Lisa誤會的表情都被捕捉下來，旁邊Jisoo也全程目睹，她疑似也笑出聲，聲音被節目收錄了進去。最近這段畫面又被韓網友挖出來，讓粉絲直呼，「Lisa可愛屎了，人類怎麼可能像她這麼可愛啦！」、「又可愛、又漂亮！」、「這段我重蕊好幾次！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5431/d5431093.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5431%2Fd5431093.gif&h=4e7678f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lisa瞬間變臉全被拍。（圖／翻攝自AbemaTV）"},{"pid":"b7c155fe929370a2e8ad50f4f4149c510f808b58","tid":2388462,"uid":256796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12eb84ff07094fb3bb58bee03169ef5f5252ac58","tid":2388462,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b7c155fe929370a2e8ad50f4f4149c510f808b58","tid":2388462,"uid":256796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:00:10.000Z","msg":"Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"太好戲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4168d7883410b14742d37f3fcd63b275a4bd3a8","tid":2388462,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"我老婆rose <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804a193ce5d688e0c6b788c4783ef4f09eeac283","tid":2388462,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4168d7883410b14742d37f3fcd63b275a4bd3a8","tid":2388462,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:02:30.000Z","msg":"我老婆rose <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"BP屈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224a266227486ff151aa8b034d836ae73ba5fb97","tid":2388462,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"勁qq...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8cfcf2c678cf1b0ad29f9361d53984d373e1bf","tid":2388462,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"224a266227486ff151aa8b034d836ae73ba5fb97","tid":2388462,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"勁qq...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class